722901f-b.title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - 90th Street (West)
722901f-b.text:
Riverside Park: The Hudson River Yacht Club at
the foot of West 90th Atreet as viewed northeastward
(No. 1) and southeastward (No. 27. Note in the latter
the Soldiers and Sailors Monument. This is on the west
side of the Drive, at 89th Street.
The numerous apartnent houses s iown forming a
''qold Coast'', line the easterly side of this thoroughfare
and overlook both the park ard the river.
July 11. 1931
Views: 1-2
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
